# Interview Prep Layout

Each track is self-contained — rules and frameworks live **inside** the track folder.

| Track | Solutions | Human reference | Cursor agent rule |
|-------|-----------|-----------------|-------------------|
| **Coding/** (DSA) | `Coding/**/*.py` | — | `Coding/.cursor/rules/problem-solving.mdc` |
| **LLD/** (low-level design) | `LLD/**/*` | `LLD/delivery-framework.md` | `LLD/.cursor/rules/design-principles.mdc` |

When working in a track, follow that folder's rule and framework. Do not mix Coding structure into LLD or vice versa.
